  "remarks": "\nMohammad Baqer ZOLQADR is an involved person within the meaning of the Iran (Sanctions) (Nuclear) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. Mohammad Baqer ZOLQADR is a member of, or associated with, a person involved in a relevant nuclear activity, namely the Islamic Revolutionary Guards Corps.\n",
